try log in first
if reset_pass_status is true 
	session data will be setup to enable only your userdata and basic data but you wont be allowed to view pages until you reset pass
	unauth page will show the reset pass page if this is the case for the user who has logged in but does not have access to page
	unauth page will redirect user back to that page until user enters in the password 
	else the user is just shown the unauth page from here 
	go to page to reset pass 
		if pass is reset correctly go to index page after data is updated
		else logout and request for a new tem password 
else 
	normal login procedures
